name: nb_anacondacloud
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.4.0" %}
{% set gh_org = "Anaconda-Platform" %}
{% set gh_repo = "nb_anacondacloud" %}

package:
  name: {{ gh_repo }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: {{ gh_repo }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  url: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}/archive/{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 3f6ab7c466d073281e05fc40937d65631c966d5ae50446ae847dd361f16bef48

build:
  number: 3
  script:
    - python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record=record.txt
    - jupyter nbextension install nb_anacondacloud --py --sys-prefix --overwrite

requirements:
  host:
    - python
    - setuptools
    - notebook >=4.3.1
    - anaconda-client

  run:
    - python
    - notebook >=4.3.1
    - nb_conda_kernels >=2.0.0
    - anaconda-client

test:
  imports:
    - nb_anacondacloud

about:
  home: https://github.com/{{ gh_org }}/{{ gh_repo }}
  license: BSD-3-Clause
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: Interact with Anaconda Cloud

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - bollwyvl
    - damianavila
